flowchart LR
    U[Main User] --> UI[Web / App Interface]
    UI --> FORM[Input / Submission Form]
    FORM --> STORE[(Data Storage)]
    STORE --> LIST[Record List]
    LIST --> DETAIL[Detail View]
    STORE --> DASH[Dashboard / Summary]
    ADMIN[Admin / Manager] --> ADMINP[Admin Panel]
    ADMINP --> STORE
    ADMINP --> STATUS[Status Update]
    STATUS --> STORE

